The paper focuses on replication strategies and their impact on data grid performance, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the use of data mining techniques to enhance replication strategies, which is related to Databases (cs.DB) and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) as data security is a concern in data grid systems. The paper also mentions the impact of replica distribution on network infrastructure (cs.NI) and proposes new evaluation metrics (cs.LG) for replication strategies.
